-------------------------------------------------------GIAI PHAP TOKEN-------------------------------------------------------
tren server co luu tru public key
tren server co luu tru cert trong he thong certmng
ung voi moi web cua khach hang co 1 serial cua token
khi thao tac ky tren 1 hoa don: 
	client gui thong tin serial len server
	noi dung cua hoa don do dang xml
	tren server se check xem dung serial do dung hay khong moi cho ban ky tren to hoa don do duoi client (phong truong hop ban vao 1 trang web cua 1 khach hang khac ban thao tac ky)
	client sau khi ky len 1 to hoa don se gui thong tin len server
		client gui xml len va bang tom luoc noi dung (digest value) va noi dung hoa don (xml invoice) len server
		clien dung private key ky len bang tom luoc roi gui len server voi noi dung (signaturevalue)
		client gui cert serial len server (x509certificate)
		server se su dung x509certificate + pass se build ra x509certificate mang pubkey ben trong

khach hang co the su dung token cua viettel de ky
khach hang cung gui thong tin cer len de server vnpt luu tru
tren server cua vnpt luu tru public key cua viettel luon

cach server verify:
	1 khach hang khi vao web portal cua vnpt de xem to hoa don do co phai do ben A ky khong
		server vnpt se dung pubkey luu tru tren server
		dung pubkey de ma hoa lai digest value
		neu digest value ma pubkey ma hoa = digest value cua prikey ma hoa (trong to hoa don do - dieu nay giong nhu viec ben A dong 1 con dau do tren to hoa don - nhiem vu vnpt la bao cho khach hang biet la to hoa don do dung la do ben cong ty A dong chu khong phai do cong ty nao do dong dau )
		thi server vnpt se noi rang to hoa don do dung la do ben A ky
		sau do server vnpt se dong 1 dau xac thuc tren to hoa don do ( dau check V )
		khach hang se vao lay to hoa don do va thay vnpt da noi rang hoa don do dung la do ben A ky roi khong sai duoc
	khach hang yen tam lay to hoa don do 
--------------------------------------------------------------GIAI PHAP HSM------------------------------------------------------
tren server luu tru san certificate trong he thong certmng bao gom luon private key lan public key
khi nguoi dung thao tac ky len 1 hoa don nao do
he thong load serial number cua trang web do chuyen doi thanh x509certificate
su dung private key co san trong he thong ky len hoa don do
luu vao xml hoa don bang (digest value)
luu vao xml hoa don signaturevalue
luu vao xml x509 certificate ( mang thong tin cua cong ty do) + password se lay len duoc x509 certificate chua pubkey trong do
server verify hoa don bang cach su dung public key luu tren server de verify theo thuan toan sha1


--------------------------------------------------------------CACH LAM------------------------------------------------------------
khi bat dau build 1 he thong cua khach hang
minh yeu cau khach hang gui cho minh 1 serial number
tren server minh se luu serial number do, tuong ung voi ten cong ty, dia chi




